provisions.content:
1. Any offence against the following sections of the Criminal Justice
(Administration) Act-
   (a) section 46 (offences under Part I1 after a second conviction of
       crime, powers of taking such offender into custody);
   (6) section 5 1 (penalty for harbouring thieves);
   (c) section 52 (assaults on police).

3. Any offence against the following sections of the Road T d E c Act-
    (a) section 34 (driving motor vehicles under influence of drink or
        drugs);
    (6) section 34A (driving or being in charge of a vehicle while blood-
        alcohol levels exceeds prescribed limit);
    (c) section 45 (unlawful user of motor vehicle);
    (6) section 46(a) (fraudulently altering or using any licence, licensing or
        registration mark or plates).
